<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f3f4f6; margin: 0; padding: 32px 16px; color: #111827; }
        .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
        .header { background: #1e293b; padding: 28px 32px; }
        .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header h1 span { color: #60a5fa; }
        .banner { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 14px 32px; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 500; }
        .body { padding: 32px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #374151; }
        .invoice-box { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .invoice-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .invoice-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 12px; }
        .label { color: #6b7280; }
        .value { color: #111827; font-weight: 500; }
        .total { color: #dc2626; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }
        .message { font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Gesto<span>Pro</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="banner">
        ⚠️ Relance — facture impayée
    </div>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="greeting">
            Bonjour {{ invoice.client.name }},
        </div>

        <p class="message">
            Sauf erreur de notre part, la facture <strong>{{ invoice.number }}</strong>
            émise par <strong>{{ user.fullName }}</strong>
            {% if invoice.dueAt %}
                et dont l'échéance était le <strong>{{ invoice.dueAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong>
            {% endif %}
            n'a pas encore été réglée.
        </p>

        <div class="invoice-box">
            <div class="invoice-row">
                <span class="label">Numéro</span>
                <span class="value">{{ invoice.number }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="invoice-row">
                <span class="label">Date d'émission</span>
                <span class="value">{{ invoice.issuedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
            </div>
            {% if invoice.dueAt %}
            <div class="invoice-row">
                <span class="label">Échéance</span>
                <span class="value" style="color:#dc2626;">{{ invoice.dueAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="invoice-row">
                <span class="label">Total TTC à régler</span>
                <span class="total">{{ invoice.totalTtc|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} {{ invoice.currency }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="message">
            Merci de procéder au règlement dans les meilleurs délais.<br>
            En cas de question ou si vous avez déjà effectué le paiement, veuillez ignorer ce message.
        </p>

        {% if reminderCount > 1 %}
        <p class="message" style="color:#dc2626;">
            Il s'agit de notre <strong>{{ reminderCount }}e relance</strong>.
        </p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        Cet email a été envoyé par {{ user.fullName }} via GestoPro.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
